I am pleased to announce the release of ^*ILearn to Play Bridge 2^*N, the latest computer program that I have developed. This program is available as a ^*Bfree^*N download through the web site of the ^*BAmerican Contract Bridge League^*N (ACBL). You can click on the yellow rectangle below to be taken to this web site in a new browser window.

|cs|1|at|^-{ ^*Hwww.acbl.org^*N }
